    <item>
      <title>对于世界上最贫穷的国家来说，特朗普关税是“灾难”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-are-disaster-for-the-world-s-poorest-countries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的新互惠关税将遭受世界上最贫穷的国家的最难打击，这使他们的劳动密集型出口行业处于危险之中，并降低了美国比竞争对手中国最大的经济优势之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-are-disaster-for-the-world-s-poorest-countries</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的互惠关税对印度意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-on-india-how-is-country-economy-impacted-what-is-modi-doing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“关税国王。”关税的“大虐待者”。一个“非常高的关税国家”。多年来，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）一再明确表示，他对印度贸易保护主义贸易政策的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-on-india-how-is-country-economy-impacted-what-is-modi-doing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:04:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因涉嫌间谍而拘留三个菲律宾人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-detains-three-filipinos-for-alleged-spying-as-ties-fray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，它拘留了三名涉嫌间谍的菲律宾国民，这一举动可能会进一步构成北京和马尼拉之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-detains-three-filipinos-for-alleged-spying-as-ties-fray</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>起亚首席执行官在特朗普的关税云美国观点时向欧洲看</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/kia-ceo-looks-to-europe-as-trump-s-tariffs-cloud-us-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[起亚公司的目标是在唐纳德·特朗普总统的汽车关税和反越门政策中销售欧洲更多的电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/kia-ceo-looks-to-europe-as-trump-s-tariffs-cloud-us-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本说，特朗普的24％关税令人失望，发誓家庭援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japan-calls-trump-s-24-tariff-regrettable-pushes-for-exemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本总理表示，在美国宣布对美国安全盟友最高的日本征收新税后，特朗普政府最新的关税范围令人失望，并发誓对国内行业的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japan-calls-trump-s-24-tariff-regrettable-pushes-for-exemption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国的目标是将贸易部长派往我们讨论关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普政府宣布向美国安全盟友征收最高的关税率之一之后，韩国的临时领导层被置于紧急模式，以保护依靠出口的经济免受贸易危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:10:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南魅力攻势未能避免46％的特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南表示，它正在采用解决方案，将特朗普政府征收的巨大关税与两国之间的良好关系“不一致”，因为魅力攻势未能避免违反白宫宣布的最大税款之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/vietnam-s-charm-offensive-fails-to-stave-off-huge-trump-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在特朗普的10％关税之后，英国继续推动贸易协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/uk-keeps-powder-dry-in-pursuit-of-deal-after-trump-s-10-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国避免报复，并将在唐纳德·特朗普总统对来自该国的所有进口的关税达到10％的关税之后，作为全球全球税的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/uk-keeps-powder-dry-in-pursuit-of-deal-after-trump-s-10-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:51:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普削弱中国海上重量的竞标需要“数十年”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-s-bid-to-weaken-china-s-maritime-heft-may-take-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据洛杉矶港口负责人的说法，特朗普政府计划挑战中国海上统治权，并通过造船业的变化迎来迎接中国的统治地位，这可能是数十年的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-s-bid-to-weaken-china-s-maritime-heft-may-take-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 05:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
